    "title": "赫兹偶极子辐射功率与辐射电阻",
    "type": "计算",
    "problem": "赫兹偶极子长度 $l=0.3\\ \\mathrm{m}$，工作频率 $f=100\\ \\mathrm{MHz}$（$\\lambda=3\\ \\mathrm{m}$），馈电电流幅值 $I_0=1\\ \\mathrm{A}$。求辐射电阻 $R_r$ 与总辐射功率 $P$。",
    "steps": [
      {
        "text": "赫兹偶极子条件 $l\\ll\\lambda$。$l/\\lambda=0.3/3=0.1\\ll 1$，满足。",
        "latex": "\\frac{l}{\\lambda}=\\frac{0.3}{3}=0.1"
      },
      {
        "text": "辐射电阻公式 $R_r=80\\pi^{2}\\!\\left(\\dfrac{l}{\\lambda}\\right)^{2}$。",
        "latex": "R_r=80\\pi^{2}\\times 0.1^{2}=0.8\\pi^{2}"
      },
      {
        "text": "代入 $\\pi^{2}\\approx 9.87$ 计算得辐射电阻。",
        "latex": "R_r\\approx 0.8\\times 9.87\\approx 7.90\\ \\Omega"
      },
      {
        "text": "辐射功率 $P=\\tfrac{1}{2}I_0^{2}R_r$（$I_0$ 为电流幅值，时间平均用 $1/2$）。",
        "latex": "P=\\frac{1}{2}I_0^{2}R_r=\\frac{1}{2}\\times 1^{2}\\times 7.90"
      },
      {
        "text": "得辐射功率。亦可由远区坡印廷矢量在球面上积分验证 $P=40\\pi^{2}\\!\\left(\\dfrac{I_0 l}{\\lambda}\\right)^{2}$。",
        "latex": "P\\approx 3.95\\ \\mathrm{W}"
      }
    ],
    "answer": "\\boxed{R_r\\approx 7.90\\ \\Omega,\\quad P\\approx 3.95\\ \\mathrm{W}}",
    "related": [
      "rad-resistance",
      "rad-power",
      "rad-dipole-far"
    ]
  },
